Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.76,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.80,0:00:21.12,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,May I recommend this slave?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.42,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,It's level 75.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.08,0:00:31.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,That's close to twenty times my level.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.47,Main,N,0,0,0,,How much for this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.47,0:00:37.70,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well, it is highly capable in battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.70,0:00:40.64,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,How does 15 gold pieces sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,Showing me your most expensive slave \Nknowing that I can't afford it, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.30,0:00:48.56,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Indeed. You're sure to become \None of my best patrons,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.56,0:00:52.36,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,so I need you to develop \Na keen eye, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.74,0:00:54.70,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.90,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen my best,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.90,0:01:01.60,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,let me ask you: what kind \Nof slave would you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,One that's cheap and obedient.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.92,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.38,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,a demi-human?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.54,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,These aren't suited for \Ncombat or manual labor.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.54,0:01:14.76,Main,N,0,0,0,,If I need them in battle, I'll train them.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.84,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,That's an amusing response,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.26,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,when you don't believe in people.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.98,Main,N,0,0,0,,But slaves aren't people.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Training one is no different \Nthan upgrading my shield.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.32,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Well, you've got me there.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.26,0:01:33.48,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,These are the cheapest \Nslaves I can offer you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.54,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,From the left...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.54,0:01:36.45,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.00,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,That half-raccoon is diseased \Nand has a mental disorder.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.46,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I'm having a real hard time with her myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.34,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Her previous owner loved \Nhis torture, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.78,0:01:57.66,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I doubt she'll last much longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.66,0:01:58.64,Main,N,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.90,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.44,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.48,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,The pain will dissipate soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.32,0:04:07.80,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,The slave crest on her chest makes \Nit impossible for her to disobey you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,"Party member settings"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.06,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,Now this girl is all yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,Thirty silvers, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.90,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,There's one extra in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,That's your commission.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.04,Main,N,0,0,0,,You were going to wring it out \Nof me anyway, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.62,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,You certainly are perceptive.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.13,Main,N,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I should know your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.18,Main,Raph,0,0,0,,R-Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.16,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.84,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to your next visit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.94,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,He really {\i1}did{\i0} choose her.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.14,Main,SlaveT,0,0,0,,I'm getting goosebumps!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.99,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.52,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.46,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... What's with the girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,Give me a weapon she can use.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.17,Main,N,0,0,0,,Keep it under six silvers.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.34,Main,R,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.60,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, draw your knife.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let me see you stab and burst this thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.28,Main,R,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.19,Main,N,0,0,0,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.36,Main,N,0,0,0,,You'll only hurt yourself by refusing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.70,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,Too weak!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.71,Main,N,0,0,0,,Put more effort into it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,Huh? I get EXP, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.52,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Probably because you set her as a\Ncompanion when forming the pact.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.64,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Wait, you didn't do that\Nwith the lady from before?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,Damn that woman...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.02,0:06:20.90,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.68,0:06:25.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,From here on out, I expect you \Nto fight monsters for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.32,Main,N,0,0,0,,I bought you with the little money I had.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,You'd better help me recoup \Nyour cost, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.80,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Kid, you ain't dyin' a pretty death.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.87,Main,N,0,0,0,,Thanks for the compliment.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Quit sitting around. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.88,Main,R,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.21,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.21,0:06:51.00,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's our country's fault, \Nor if the kid's just gone bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,Three silvers left...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.46,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.70,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,We don't have all day, you little shits!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.48,Main,Merch,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, you moron?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.78,Main,Slave,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.66,Main,N,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.20,Main,R,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,You can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,Let's get some lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.62,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\an8}U-Um...{an8 cause of ts}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.62,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.38,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\an8}This place...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.10,Main,G,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.66,Main,G,0,0,0,,Ugh, it's the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.14,Main,G,0,0,0,,Is he the rapist?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.60,Main,G,0,0,0,,Keep it down! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,Can I order?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.92,Main,G,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.92,0:07:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.64,Main,W,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look, it's a demi-human.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.32,Main,G,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why's she here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.19,Main,N,0,0,0,,The cheapest lunch set you have.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.24,Main,G,0,0,0,,Someone kick her out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.90,Main,N,0,0,0,,And she'll have whatever that kid's having.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.90,Main,G,0,0,0,,That'll be nine coppers.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.40,Main,N,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.14,Main,R,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,Did you want something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.58,Main,R,0,0,0,,Why are you getting it for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,Because you looked like \Nyou wanted to try it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.02,Main,G,0,0,0,,Here's your food.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.60,Main,N,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.01,Main,R,0,0,0,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yes, just eat up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.34,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.94,0:08:46.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.25,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,I still can't taste a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.43,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.06,Main,R,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.64,0:09:08.60,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,Blending ability, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,That might come in handy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.56,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.71,Main,R,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.04,Main,N,0,0,0,,A hero. The shield one.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.04,0:09:36.26,Main,R,0,0,0,,You mean... One of the Four Great Heroes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.26,0:09:36.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.39,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.85,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,Do you know of the four legendary heroes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.14,0:09:48.10,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yep! The sword one, \Nthe bow one, the spear one,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.73,Main,R,0,0,0,,And the one with the shield!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.18,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.18,0:09:56.36,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,The Shield Hero, in particular, \Ntreated us demi-humans very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.20,Main,R,0,0,0,,Really? I'd like to meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.86,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,If you're a good girl, I'm sure \Nyou'll meet him one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.46,Main,R,0,0,0,,The Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.76,Main,R,0,0,0,,U-Um... What is your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.84,Main,N,0,0,0,,Iwatani Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.96,Main,R,0,0,0,,Iwatani... Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.31,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's a medicine I blended.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,Apparently, it can cure mild colds.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.69,Main,R,0,0,0,,So bitter!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.98,Main,N,0,0,0,,Good medicine tastes bitter.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.98,0:10:39.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,Just drink it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.18,Main,RDad,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.24,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,We want you to live, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.24,0:11:13.15,Main,RMom,0,0,0,,Please forgive our selfishness.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.78,Main,R,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.52,Main,R,0,0,0,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.42,Main,N,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.32,Main,N,0,0,0,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.42,0:11:30.50,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\an8}No... Help...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.50,0:11:35.28,Main,R,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! Dad, Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.96,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.38,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,The quality's not bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.10,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Are you well versed in\N making medicines, Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Yesterday was my first try.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.56,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.02,Main,N,0,0,0,,Which is more profitable, \Nselling herbs or medicine?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.28,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,Due to the Wave's impact,\N medicine is flying off the shelves lately,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.64,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,so I'd pay more for medicine than for herbs.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.99,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.24,Main,Herbist,0,0,0,,In total, this is worth four silvers.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,Say, do you have any tools \Nyou don't use anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.78,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.54,Main,Kid2,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.60,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.18,0:12:18.67,Main,Kid1,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.26,Main,N,0,0,0,,Do you want one of those balls?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.00,Main,R,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.34,Main,R,0,0,0,,I don't want one at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.85,Main,N,0,0,0,,So she wants one, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.10,Main,N,0,0,0,,You can play with it {\i1}after{\i0}\Nwe're done with work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.23,Main,R,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.32,Main,G,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.60,Main,G,0,0,0,,{Uh, }The Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.60,0:12:46.26,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'd like to rent a room.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.48,Main,N,0,0,0,,My companion might cry out at night, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.87,Main,N,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} let us stay, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.92,Main,G,0,0,0,,O-Of course! I'll prepare a room at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.50,0:13:04.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,I have to find a way to survive before \Nthe next Wave of Catastrophe hits.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.40,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right. We can go a little \Ndeeper into the forest now...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.47,Main,N,0,0,0,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.39,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now, Raphtalia! Stab it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.48,Main,N,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Get on with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.56,Main,R,0,0,0,,B-But... It'll bleed if I do...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.74,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.78,Main,R,0,0,0,,I'm scared of blood!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.99,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.70,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't fight, then I won't be \Nable to look after you anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,A Wave that threatens the world's \Nexistence is coming soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.54,Main,N,0,0,0,,I have to get as strong \Nas I can before it does.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.08,Main,N,0,0,0,,But defense is all I'm good for.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.46,Main,N,0,0,0,,I need someone to fight for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't do it, I'll get someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.06,Main,R,0,0,0,,You're going to fight the Catastrophe?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.97,Main,N,0,0,0,,That is my job.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.35,Main,R,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.04,0:14:55.40,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master... I'll fight for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.46,Main,R,0,0,0,,So please don't abandon me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.30,Main,N,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.90,Main,N,0,0,0,,Not a game.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.16,Main,N,0,0,0,,If I want to live, I have \Nno choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.39,Main,N,0,0,0,,Sell us a new weapon for this much.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.78,0:15:16.88,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Time to get the little miss a sword, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.94,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,One on the short side would \Nbe good to start off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.86,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.34,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,It's a short sword made of iron.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.00,Main,N,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is there a town or village nearby that \Nwe can travel to with our equipment?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.70,0:15:36.34,Main,Erh,0,0,0,,Well, with your stuff, it'd have to be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.06,Main,N,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.06,0:15:45.46,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Around two silvers in all, I'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.68,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.68,0:15:50.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know of any spots nearby \Nwhen you can earn a lot of money quick?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.92,0:15:57.98,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The ores from that coal pit over there \Nshould fetch a decent amount, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is there a catch?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.50,0:16:05.06,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Ever since the first Wave, it's become \Nhome to a bunch of dangerous monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.40,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Nobody dares approach it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.88,0:16:13.30,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Sheesh! I don't know what those\Nheroes they summoned are even doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's got an exclusive effect and skill?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.24,Main,N,0,0,0,,Rope Shield...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Just what it sounds like, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.20,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.66,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.10,Main,N,0,0,0,,There are dangerous \Nmonsters here, apparently.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.26,Main,N,0,0,0,,The moment things go south, we run.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Make sure to keep up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.21,Main,R,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.02,Main,R,0,0,0,,U-{\alpha&HFF&}Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.02,0:17:06.80,Main,R,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.22,Main,N,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.22,0:17:12.42,Main,R,0,0,0,,How should I address you, Master?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,Call me whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.43,Main,R,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.47,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.36,Main,R,0,0,0,,Are those...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.12,Main,N,0,0,0,,This will fetch a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, let's try over there next...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.54,Main,R,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.98,Main,R,0,0,0,,A d-dog monster...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.86,Main,R,0,0,0,,Killed all the villagers, \Neven Dad and Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.57,Main,N,0,0,0,,During the first Wave, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,So that's why she starts \Ncrying every night.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.88,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is that the same dog that \Nkilled your parents?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.58,Main,R,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.62,Main,N,0,0,0,,Listen, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.50,Main,N,0,0,0,,Take that thing out here and now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.38,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you fight and make me stronger,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.89,Main,N,0,0,0,,we can fend off the Waves of Catastrophe \Nand prevent that tragedy from reoccurring.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.06,Main,N,0,0,0,,Your parents won't ever come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.06,0:18:47.85,Main,N,0,0,0,,But we can prevent other kids \Nfrom going through what you did.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.24,0:18:53.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,And all I'm capable of is making \Nsure you can fight as best you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now, Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.72,Main,N,0,0,0,,Stab it with your sword!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.45,Main,N,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.52,Main,R,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.08,Main,N,0,0,0,,If I die, so will you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.96,Main,R,0,0,0,,Please no!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.96,Main,N,0,0,0,,Then hurry up and kill it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.42,Main,N,0,0,0,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.69,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia, forget it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.48,Main,N,0,0,0,,If you can't fight, then get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.65,Main,R,0,0,0,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.92,Main,N,0,0,0,,I'll buy time for you to escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.92,0:19:44.91,Main,R,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.37,Main,R,0,0,0,,That'd be
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,just like then...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.66,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.18,Main,R,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.04,0:19:56.67,Main,N,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.76,Main,N,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.10,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.86,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.32,Main,N,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.26,Main,N,0,0,0,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.95,Main,N,0,0,0,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.78,Main,N,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.54,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.30,0:20:56.02,Main,N,0,0,0,,Hey, even with the shield's power,\N the wound still hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.82,Main,R,0,0,0,,Don't ever die! Please don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.88,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.95,Main,N,0,0,0,,She chose my name, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.06,0:21:08.24,Main,N,0,0,0,,You attack, and I defend.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.94,Main,N,0,0,0,,That way, neither of us will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.79,Main,R,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.82,0:21:15.82,Main,N,0,0,0,,We're leaving once I feed \Nthis monster to my shield.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.32,Main,R,0,0,0,,Okay, Naofumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.24,Main,N,0,0,0,,Get off already.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.54,Main,R,0,0,0,,A bit longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.70,0:23:04.36,Main,N,0,0,0,,The ore made us a lot of money, \Nso you can eat all you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.36,0:23:05.15,Main,R,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.12,0:23:08.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.18,Main,R,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.12,Main,N,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.26,0:23:16.16,Main,R,0,0,0,,Naofumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.34,0:23:20.58,Main,R,0,0,0,,Let's survive, no matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.28,Main,N,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.58,Main,N,0,0,0,,Here. A kids' meal...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.96,0:23:30.52,Main,N,0,0,0,,isn't complete without this.
